runexp /kst/exp/taro/taro 6:20 convN 3P

Measurements of the dayside plasma convection poleward of the open-closed field
line boundary. Coordination with the Geotail satellite, Jicamarca ISR and Poker
Flat AMISR to relate the dayside convection to prompt penetration electric
fields and changes in the IMF and the solar wind dynamic pressure,

